<li id="cite_note-supervisor-43"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-supervisor_43-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The highest privilege level has various names throughout different architectures, such as supervisor mode, kernel mode, CPL0, DPL0, Ring 0, etc. See <a href="Ring_(computer_security).html" title="Ring (computer security)">Ring (computer security)</a> for more information.</span></li>
